---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About - Portfolio"
	description="Learn more about my background, skills, and experience"
>
	<article>
		<h1
			class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
		>
			About Me
		</h1>

		<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
			<p
				class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-loose mb-6"
			>
				I am polyglot developer with {new Date().getFullYear() - 2004} years
				of experience, I've been all over the place but TypeScript and React
				has been the bulk of my latest experiences lately.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-loose">
				I started working when I was 15 years old with a PHP book and a
				Technical Degree, eventually I learned a lot by doing. I was
				able to fit a Baschelor on computer science and one of Science
				and technology while still working. I had a broad career seeing
				technologies bloom and fade away, and adapting myself at every
				step.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-loose">
				Currently I value testing, a tight feedback loop, and
				experimental development. Developers should be able to test
				their hypothesis often, safely and quickly. A fast and safe Dev
				is a happy dev.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-loose">
				On a personal level I enjoy close-up Magic, Bouldering, Board
				games and nice beers.
			</p>
		</div>

		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
				Current Stack
			</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
				>
					<h3
						class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
					>
						Frontend
					</h3>
					<ul
						class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1"
					>
						<li>React</li>
						<li>CSS</li>
						<li>Cypress</li>
						<li>Storybook</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
				>
					<h3
						class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
					>
						Backend
					</h3>
					<ul
						class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1"
					>
						<li>Next.js</li>
						<li>NestJs</li>
						<li>PostgreSQL</li>
						<li>Graphql</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
				>
					<h3
						class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
					>
						Infrastructure
					</h3>
					<ul
						class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1"
					>
						<li>CDK</li>
						<li>Docker</li>
						<li>AWS</li>
						<li>Testing</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
				Current position
			</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="border-l-4 border-gray-900 dark:border-white pl-6">
					<h3
						class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
					>
						Staff Engineer
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">
						Taxdoo â€¢ January 2025 - Present
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
						Leading development of modern web applications using
						React and TypeScript. Collaborating with
						cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software
						solutions.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="mt-12">
			<a
				href="/cv"
				class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-500 focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
			>
				View Full CV
			</a>
		</div>
	</article>
</BaseLayout>
